{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.1","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:1","prev_osis_id":"Dan.005.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Daniel dans la fosse aux lions<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-24: cf. (Da 3. H\u00e9 11:32-34.) (Est 7:9, 10. Ps 7:15-18.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Darius trouva bon d\u2019\u00e9tablir sur le royaume cent vingt satrapes, qui devaient \u00eatre dans tout le royaume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.2","name":"Daniel 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.5.31","name":"Daniel 5:31","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.5.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.2","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:2","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il mit \u00e0 leur t\u00eate trois chefs, au nombre desquels \u00e9tait Daniel, afin que ces satrapes leur rendissent compte, et que le roi ne souffr\u00eet aucun dommage.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.3","name":"Daniel 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.1","name":"Daniel 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.3","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:3","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Daniel surpassait les chefs et les satrapes, parce qu\u2019il y avait en lui un esprit sup\u00e9rieur; et le roi pensait \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tablir sur tout le royaume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.4","name":"Daniel 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.2","name":"Daniel 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.4","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:4","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Alors les chefs et les satrapes cherch\u00e8rent une occasion d\u2019accuser Daniel en ce qui concernait les affaires du royaume. Mais ils ne purent trouver aucune occasion, ni aucune chose \u00e0 reprendre, parce qu\u2019il \u00e9tait fid\u00e8le, et qu\u2019on n\u2019apercevait chez lui ni faute, ni rien de mauvais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.5","name":"Daniel 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.3","name":"Daniel 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.5","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:5","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Et ces hommes dirent: Nous ne trouverons aucune occasion contre ce Daniel, \u00e0 moins que nous n\u2019en trouvions une dans la loi de son Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.6","name":"Daniel 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.4","name":"Daniel 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.6","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:6","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Puis ces chefs et ces satrapes se rendirent tumultueusement aupr\u00e8s du roi, et lui parl\u00e8rent ainsi: Roi Darius, vis \u00e9ternellement!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.7","name":"Daniel 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.5","name":"Daniel 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.7","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:7","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Tous les chefs du royaume, les intendants, les satrapes, les conseillers, et les gouverneurs sont d\u2019avis qu\u2019il soit publi\u00e9 un \u00e9dit royal, avec une d\u00e9fense s\u00e9v\u00e8re, portant que quiconque, dans l\u2019espace de trente jours, adressera des pri\u00e8res \u00e0 quelque dieu ou \u00e0 quelque homme, except\u00e9 \u00e0 toi, \u00f4 roi, sera jet\u00e9 dans la fosse aux lions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.8","name":"Daniel 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.6","name":"Daniel 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.8","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:8","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Maintenant, \u00f4 roi, confirme la d\u00e9fense, et \u00e9cris le d\u00e9cret, afin qu\u2019il soit irr\u00e9vocable, selon la loi des M\u00e8des et des Perses, qui est immuable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.9","name":"Daniel 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.7","name":"Daniel 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.9","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:9","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>L\u00e0-dessus le roi Darius \u00e9crivit le d\u00e9cret et la d\u00e9fense.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.10","name":"Daniel 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.8","name":"Daniel 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.10","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:10","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Lorsque Daniel sut que le d\u00e9cret \u00e9tait \u00e9crit, il se retira dans sa maison, o\u00f9 les fen\u00eatres de la chambre sup\u00e9rieure \u00e9taient ouvertes dans la direction de J\u00e9rusalem; et trois fois le jour il se mettait \u00e0 genoux, il priait, et il louait son Dieu, comme il le faisait auparavant.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.11","name":"Daniel 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.9","name":"Daniel 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.11","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:11","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Alors ces hommes entr\u00e8rent tumultueusement, et ils trouv\u00e8rent Daniel qui priait et invoquait son Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.12","name":"Daniel 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.10","name":"Daniel 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.12","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:12","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Puis ils se pr\u00e9sent\u00e8rent devant le roi, et lui dirent au sujet de la d\u00e9fense royale: N\u2019as-tu pas \u00e9crit une d\u00e9fense portant que quiconque dans l\u2019espace de trente jours adresserait des pri\u00e8res \u00e0 quelque dieu ou \u00e0 quelque homme, except\u00e9 \u00e0 toi, \u00f4 roi, serait jet\u00e9 dans la fosse aux lions? Le roi r\u00e9pondit: La chose est certaine, selon la loi des M\u00e8des et des Perses, qui est immuable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.13","name":"Daniel 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.11","name":"Daniel 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.13","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:13","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils prirent de nouveau la parole et dirent au roi: Daniel, l\u2019un des captifs de Juda, n\u2019a tenu aucun compte de toi, \u00f4 roi, ni de la d\u00e9fense que tu as \u00e9crite, et il fait sa pri\u00e8re trois fois le jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.14","name":"Daniel 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.12","name":"Daniel 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.14","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:14","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Le roi fut tr\u00e8s afflig\u00e9 quand il entendit cela; il prit \u00e0 c\u0153ur de d\u00e9livrer Daniel, et jusqu\u2019au coucher du soleil il s\u2019effor\u00e7a de le sauver.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.15","name":"Daniel 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.13","name":"Daniel 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.15","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:15","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mais ces hommes insist\u00e8rent aupr\u00e8s du roi, et lui dirent: Sache, \u00f4 roi, que la loi des M\u00e8des et des Perses exige que toute d\u00e9fense ou tout d\u00e9cret confirm\u00e9 par le roi soit irr\u00e9vocable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.16","name":"Daniel 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.14","name":"Daniel 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.16","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:16","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Alors le roi donna l\u2019ordre qu\u2019on amen\u00e2t Daniel, et qu\u2019on le jet\u00e2t dans la fosse aux lions. Le roi prit la parole et dit \u00e0 Daniel: Puisse ton Dieu, que tu sers avec pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance, te d\u00e9livrer!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.17","name":"Daniel 6:17","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.15","name":"Daniel 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.17","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:17","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>On apporta une pierre, et on la mit sur l\u2019ouverture de la fosse; le roi la scella de son anneau et de l\u2019anneau de ses grands, afin que rien ne f\u00fbt chang\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de Daniel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.18","name":"Daniel 6:18","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.16","name":"Daniel 6:16","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.18","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:18","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Le roi se rendit ensuite dans son palais; il passa la nuit \u00e0 jeun, il ne fit point venir de concubine aupr\u00e8s de lui, et il ne put se livrer au sommeil.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.19","name":"Daniel 6:19","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.17","name":"Daniel 6:17","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.19","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:19","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le roi se leva au point du jour, avec l\u2019aurore, et il alla pr\u00e9cipitamment \u00e0 la fosse aux lions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.20","name":"Daniel 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.18","name":"Daniel 6:18","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.20","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:20","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>En s\u2019approchant de la fosse, il appela Daniel d\u2019une voix triste. Le roi prit la parole et dit \u00e0 Daniel: Daniel, serviteur du Dieu vivant, ton Dieu, que tu sers avec pers\u00e9v\u00e9rance, a-t-il pu te d\u00e9livrer des lions?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.21","name":"Daniel 6:21","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.19","name":"Daniel 6:19","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.21","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:21","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et Daniel dit au roi: Roi, vis \u00e9ternellement?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.22","name":"Daniel 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.20","name":"Daniel 6:20","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.22","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:22","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Mon Dieu a envoy\u00e9 son ange et ferm\u00e9 la gueule des lions, qui ne m\u2019ont fait aucun mal, parce que j\u2019ai \u00e9t\u00e9 trouv\u00e9 innocent devant lui; et devant toi non plus, \u00f4 roi, je n\u2019ai rien fait de mauvais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.23","name":"Daniel 6:23","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.21","name":"Daniel 6:21","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.23","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:23","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Alors le roi fut tr\u00e8s joyeux, et il ordonna qu\u2019on f\u00eet sortir Daniel de la fosse. Daniel fut retir\u00e9 de la fosse, et on ne trouva sur lui aucune blessure, parce qu\u2019il avait eu confiance en son Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.24","name":"Daniel 6:24","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.22","name":"Daniel 6:22","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.24","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:24","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Le roi ordonna que ces hommes qui avaient accus\u00e9 Daniel fussent amen\u00e9s et jet\u00e9s dans la fosse aux lions, eux, leurs enfants et leurs femmes; et avant qu\u2019ils fussent parvenus au fond de la fosse, les lions les saisirent et bris\u00e8rent tous leurs os.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.25","name":"Daniel 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.23","name":"Daniel 6:23","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.25","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:25","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-28: cf. Da 3:28, 29. Ps 29:1.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s cela, le roi Darius \u00e9crivit \u00e0 tous les peuples, \u00e0 toutes les nations, aux hommes de toutes langues, qui habitaient sur toute la terre: Que la paix vous soit donn\u00e9e avec abondance!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.26","name":"Daniel 6:26","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.24","name":"Daniel 6:24","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.26","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:26","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>J\u2019ordonne que, dans toute l\u2019\u00e9tendue de mon royaume, on ait de la crainte et de la frayeur pour le Dieu de Daniel. Car il est le Dieu vivant, et il subsiste \u00e9ternellement; son royaume ne sera jamais d\u00e9truit, et sa domination durera jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la fin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.27","name":"Daniel 6:27","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.25","name":"Daniel 6:25","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.27","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:27","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.006.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>C\u2019est lui qui d\u00e9livre et qui sauve, qui op\u00e8re des signes et des prodiges dans les cieux et sur la terre. C\u2019est lui qui a d\u00e9livr\u00e9 Daniel de la puissance des lions.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.28","name":"Daniel 6:28","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.26","name":"Daniel 6:26","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.28","label":"","reference":"Daniel 6:28","prev_osis_id":"Dan.006.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Dan.007.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Dan.6.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Daniel prosp\u00e9ra sous le r\u00e8gne de Darius, et sous le r\u00e8gne de Cyrus, le Perse.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Dan.6","name":"Daniel 6","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.7.1","name":"Daniel 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.7.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Dan.6.27","name":"Daniel 6:27","id":"fra-LSG:Dan.6.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc3afac99.76470105');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc3afac99.76470105\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc3afac99.76470105","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc3afac99.76470105'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc3afac99.76470105\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}